THIRD-PARTY NOTICES (Run A only; Run B and later models are not listed here)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following services or resources are used by this project and require
copyright / usage / restriction notices. Respect is given to the original
authors and licensors.

1. Audio model used in Run A (speech emotion recognition)
   - Name: wav2vec2-lg-xlsr-en-speech-emotion-recognition
   - Author: Enrique Hernández Calabrés (ehcalabres)
   - Source: https://huggingface.co/ehcalabres/wav2vec2-lg-xlsr-en-speech-emotion-recognition
   - License: Apache License 2.0
   - Base model: jonatasgrosman/wav2vec2-large-xlsr-53-english (Wav2Vec 2.0)
   - Training data: RAVDESS (Ryerson Audio-Visual Database of Emotional Speech
     and Song), https://zenodo.org/record/1188976
   - This model is loaded from Hugging Face Hub at runtime when Run A is
     executed. It is not bundled with this repository. Use and redistribution
     of the model are governed by its Apache-2.0 license and the Hugging Face
     terms of use.

2. Hugging Face
   - This project uses the Hugging Face Hub and Transformers to load the
     above audio model (Run A). Usage is subject to Hugging Face’s terms and
     conditions: https://huggingface.co/terms

